{
  "stem": "15732.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The elderly people-- we had a library, and the elderly people were reading books.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The elderly people were organized in political-- the political parties that were Israel were sent so-called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they organized that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Whoever-- my father joined the [NON-ENGLISH] because he was in before the war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And different people did different.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were others who didn't want to do anything, because they were completely apathetic and completely passive.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And to-- to go from a-- from years of concentration camp or German oppression and to come to freedom, you have even to adjust yourself to freedom slowly.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were in Foehrenwald from-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] oh, just one minute-- from November '45 'til 1947.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I think it was June 1947 that we went illegal to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I schlepped my father and my mother again, as usual.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that stage, I told him he should stay in Foehrenwald and I will go to Israel and then I can send him a certificate.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But what my father said was, what Hitler didn't succeed, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't want now to happen.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If Hitler has not succeeded in tearing us apart, I don't want-- I will go with you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was no way of stopping me, so my father just had to go.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I was a horrible person, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At that time, I already know my husband.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, my husband-to-be I knew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You met him in--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I met Shmuelik in January 1946, on the 13th of January.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's a date I do remember for a change.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was at that time-- he arrived at that kibbutz-- at a kibbutz in Foehrenwald.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just by chance, he took Foehrenwald.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And just by chance, he came on that kibbutz where I happened to come.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
